293
00:25:56,570 --> 00:26:00,510
This is it. We can't get involved more.

294
00:26:00,510 --> 00:26:02,400
We have to go back.

295
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:04,800
Not now.

296
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:07,860
We get trapped here forever if we don't go back tonight.

297
00:26:07,860 --> 00:26:11,330
