301
00:26:18,370 --> 00:26:19,670
Travel to the past again?

302
00:26:19,670 --> 00:26:22,710
Will you go further back if something changes again?

303
00:26:22,710 --> 00:26:24,260
Come to your senses.

304
00:26:24,260 --> 00:26:26,290
2023 is the year you're going back to.

305
00:26:26,290 --> 00:26:28,370
How am I supposed to go back?

306
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:33,430
My dad's life was ruined because of me.

307
00:26:33,430 --> 00:26:36,160
I couldn't change anything.

308
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:44,720
