310
00:26:48,590 --> 00:26:50,960
Of course, you changed something.

311
00:26:53,340 --> 00:26:55,460
You saved me.

312
00:26:57,970 --> 00:27:00,680
And you saved Cheong Ah.

313
00:27:23,890 --> 00:27:27,710
 Lee Chan, I'm going on a trip with Dad. 

