00:31:17,250 --> 00:31:21,130
No one can live your life for you.

356
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:28,140
Let Lee Chan of 1995 take care of himself in 1995

357
00:31:28,140 --> 00:31:30,750
and just have faith in him.

358
00:31:30,750 --> 00:31:35,000
There are Lee Chan and Cheong Ah in 2023, too.

359
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:37,550
There's Eun Ho, too.

